### Test Controller APIs
### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7189

###############################################################################
# TEST API 1: Schema Indexing to Qdrant
###############################################################################

### 1. Test Schema Indexing (Public API - No Auth Required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test/test-schema-indexing
Content-Type: application/json

# This API will:
# - Test connection to Server=.;Database=TextToSqlTest;User Id=sa;Password=123
# - Scan database schema (tables, columns, relationships)
# - Index schema information to Qdrant vector database
# - Return detailed results of each step

###############################################################################
# TEST API 2: Query Processing Test
###############################################################################

# IMPORTANT: Two different query processing endpoints:
#
# 1. /api/test/test-query (Basic Test)
#    - Tests database connection
#    - Retrieves schema from Qdrant
#    - Lists available tables
#    - Provides query recommendations
#    - Does NOT generate or execute SQL
#
# 2. /api/test/process-query (Complete Processing - Like Console Project)
#    - Uses the full EnhancedAgentOrchestrator pipeline
#    - Validates query relevance
#    - Loads database schema
#    - Performs RAG schema retrieval
#    - Analyzes intent
#    - Generates SQL with context
#    - Validates SQL safety
#    - Executes SQL with self-correction
#    - Formats intelligent answer
#    - Returns complete results with actual data
#
# Use process-query to get the same behavior as the Console project!

### 2. Test Query - Customers (Basic - Connection & Schema Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test/test-query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show me all customers"
}

### 2b. Process Complete Query - Customers (Like Console Project - Generates SQL & Executes)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test/process-query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show me all customers"
}

### 3. Test Query - Orders (Basic)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test/test-query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Get all orders from last month"
}

